etomica.data

Class DataProcessorFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.DataProcessor
      • etomica.data.DataProcessorFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataPipe, IDataSink

    public class DataProcessorFunction
extends DataProcessor
    Applies a simple scalar function to all elements of the Data that passes through. Function is set at construction and cannot be subsequently changed.
